      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPIRIT OF ANARCHY NZ (8) crosses the border and brings some decent form from Victoria where he came from this barrier to win two back at Melton. Should enjoy a nice trail early and the sprint lane may come in handy. Finds a suitable assignment and has strong claims. LOCHINVAR MAGIC (4) showed great determination at his latest appearance at Gawler when he scored by a head after being handy in the run. Owns a strong record at this distance and should be at his peak third-up so could get the job done again. HASTY BID (1) has come from this barrier for fourth at his last two outings at this circuit and distance. Can play a role again. CLASSIC LINE (6) won the last two times he raced here so deserves respect.",
